## Resources

- **Yu-kai Chou:** *Actionable Gamification* — Octalysis framework, right-brain vs left-brain drives
- **Nir Eyal:** *Hooked* — habit loops, internal triggers, ethics of persuasion
- **BJ Fogg:** *Tiny Habits* — behavior = motivation × ability × prompt, simplicity beats willpower
- **Deci & Ryan:** *Why We Do What We Do* — intrinsic vs extrinsic motivation, SDT foundations
- **FCA Research:** *Gaming Trading* (2022) — what NOT to do in fintech gamification

When adding new features, reference these frameworks. If a feature doesn't map to a core drive or psychological need, question whether it belongs.
